    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "oh really? i've heard grapefruit is actually super healthy for your heart though. i mean it's just fruit, right? surely a little bit of juice isn't going to do anything serious to my meds. i've taken it before with a small amount and felt fine. is it actually a big deal or are people just being extra?",
